Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.30,0:24:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.32,0:24:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.41,0:24:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ezope!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2300)}Touyo.
